---
// No hay imports de React ni de lucide-react
// Los íconos se incluyen como SVG inline
---

<section class="py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, hsl(0 0% 100%) 0%, hsl(210 30% 98%) 100%);">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-fade-in">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] mb-4">
        ¿Por Qué Elegirnos?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)] max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Somos tu mejor opción porque conectamos tu necesidad con el profesional ideal: calificado, con experiencia y con certificación verificable.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div
        class="p-6 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_-5px_hsl(210_20%_20%_/_0.12)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] bg-[hsl(0_0%_100%)]"
        style="animation-delay: 0ms;"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.1)] flex items-center justify-center">
              <!-- Users Icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%)]">
                <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] flex items-center gap-2">
              <!-- Check Icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5 text-[hsl(145_60%_45%)] flex-shrink-0">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Pago directo al profesional, finalizando turno
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)] leading-relaxed">
               precios justos para ti y dignidad laboral para ellos
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div
        class="p-6 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_-5px_hsl(210_20%_20%_/_0.12)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] bg-[hsl(0_0%_100%)]"
        style="animation-delay: 100ms;"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.1)] flex items-center justify-center">
              <!-- DollarSign Icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%)]">
                <line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="22"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5 text-[hsl(145_60%_45%)] flex-shrink-0">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Hasta 50% más económico
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)] leading-relaxed">
              Que las empresas tradicionales, sin sacrificar la calidad del servicio
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div
        class="p-6 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_-5px_hsl(210_20%_20%_/_0.12)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] bg-[hsl(0_0%_100%)]"
        style="animation-delay: 200ms;"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.1)] flex items-center justify-center">
              <!-- Shield Icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%)]">
                <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5 text-[hsl(145_60%_45%)] flex-shrink-0">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Totalmente legal
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)] leading-relaxed">
              Todos los enfermeros están legalmente habilitados, con registro ante el Ministerio de Salud
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4 -->
      <div
        class="p-6 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_-5px_hsl(210_20%_20%_/_0.12)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] bg-[hsl(0_0%_100%)]"
        style="animation-delay: 300ms;"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.1)] flex items-center justify-center">
              <!-- Clock Icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%)]">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5 text-[hsl(145_60%_45%)] flex-shrink-0">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Atención personalizada
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)] leading-relaxed">
              8 o 12 horas diarias, adaptada a tus necesidades reales
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 5 -->
      <div
        class="p-6 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_-5px_hsl(210_20%_20%_/_0.12)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] bg-[hsl(0_0%_100%)]"
        style="animation-delay: 400ms;"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.1)] flex items-center justify-center">
              <!-- Award Icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%)]">
                <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="7"/><polyline points="8.21 13.89 7 23 12 20 17 23 15.79 13.88"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5 text-[hsl(145_60%_45%)] flex-shrink-0">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Especializados en post-cirugía
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)] leading-relaxed">
              Experiencia en recuperación post-cirugía estética, ideal para pacientes internacionales
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 6 -->
      <div
        class="p-6 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_-5px_hsl(210_20%_20%_/_0.12)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] bg-[hsl(0_0%_100%)]"
        style="animation-delay: 500ms;"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.1)] flex items-center justify-center">
              <!-- Heart Icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%)]">
                <path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.29 1.51 4.04 3 5.5l7 7Z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5 text-[hsl(145_60%_45%)] flex-shrink-0">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Compromiso ético
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)] leading-relaxed">
              Proyecto sin ánimo de lucro que prioriza el bienestar humano sobre las ganancias
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fade-in {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes slide-up {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fade-in 0.6s ease-out forwards;
  }
  .animate-slide-up {
    animation: slide-up 0.6s ease-out forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }
</style>